extendedInfo.description: The most realistic anti-terrorist FPS game on Android !!,In the 21st century,terrorism spreads rapidly around the whole world.As the anti-terrorism materials show that all these terrorist activities are related to a dark forces.They have quite advanced military weapons in this modern war combat: unmanned fighter, new rocket launchers, powerful machine guns, and may even have begun to take shape of nuclear weapons.In the face of this powerful dard forces,all countries get together and establish a SWAT of United Nations focusing on hitting dark forces all over the world and safeguarding world peace.Featuresï¼1  New collection and upgrade systemï¼2  New super weaponï¼3  Epic audio-visual effectsï¼4  New lifelike scenes.5  New combinations of fights!

reviews.title: Best app I have come across!
reviews.comment: I was always skeptical about free shoot em ups, but the moment I played this, I knew it was golden. There are cool guns and upgrades that you V Can buy, and even a second weapon with gold. This is the closest to being realistic I have seen in an android app.  I personally think it would be better if the aiming let you turn, but this is definitely the best free app I have come across. I definitely recommend this app
